data.description: Wonderful townhome in the quiet, yet friendly secluded Stage Coach Village community! 2 bedroom, 1.5 baths with a surprisingly amount of storage. Lovely kitchen with granite countertops! No Carpet!  lovely bamboo flooring! Updated bathrooms! Private patio allows for outdoor living and entertaining. So much charm in this home and this neighborhood, yet very close to EVERYTHING!  Desirable 27410 zip code, just minutes to shopping, dining, and Guilford College. Convenient to interstates. Don't miss this one!  Schedule your showing today!
